Core Operators
Operator	Description	Example
site:	Target specific domain/subdomain	site:example.com
site:dev.example.com
inurl:	URL contains string	inurl:/admin
inurl:.php?id=
intitle:	Page title contains string	intitle:"index of"
intitle:login
intext:	Body text contains string	intext:"error"
intext:"password"
filetype:	Specific file type	filetype:pdf
filetype:env
ext:	File extension	ext:log
ext:sql
cache:	Show cached version	cache:example.com
Boolean Logic
Operator	Function	Example
(space)	AND	site:example.com filetype:pdf
OR	OR	login OR signin
-	NOT (exclude)	site:example.com -www
Common Recon Combinations
text
site:target.com intitle:login
site:target.com inurl:/admin
site:target.com filetype:env
site:target.com ext:sql
site:target.com intitle:"index of"
site:target.com intext:"error"
site:target.com -inurl:www
site:target.com inurl:.php?id=
Pro Tips
Use "exact phrases" for precise matches

Combine operators for narrow results

Wildcards: site:*.example.com (unreliable)

Test operators individually first

Note: link: and related: operators are deprecated.

